  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "F&B Executive",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description & Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Responsible for all aspects of operation of the vaious F&B outlets assigned with standards and excellent service</li><li>Active role to contribute to the P&L and financial targets of the F&B Department</li><li>Uplift customer's dining experience creating good memories</li><li>Nurture customers' relationship and attend to customer complaints/ queries promptly</li><li>Serve promptly and efficiently</li><li>Ensure minimum wastage, breakage and spoilage</li><li>Support manpower deployment and rostering</li><li>Upsell to achieve sales and revenue targets</li><li>Oversee collection and stock control consistently according to company policies and SOPs</li><li>Pair food with drinks and make recommendations accordingly</li><li>Collaborate as a team to achieve operations efectiveness</li><li>Support Club events and ad-hoc duties assigned</li></ul><p>Requirements</p><ul><li>Minimum 1 year experience in related industry</li><li>Commitment to quality service, and food and beverage knowledge</li><li>Able to work shift hours</li><li>Able to start within short notice</li></ul><p><strong>Others:</strong></p><p>Daily 2-way Transport provided at Caldecott/Bishan MRT</p><p>Direct to MRT/home for late hours.</p><p>Uniform and meals provided</p>",
